"Dr. Amit Maheshwari is an award winning Global Business Trainer, Corporate Trainer, Keynote Motivational Speaker, Brand Consultant and Mentor and travels the world sharing his knowledge and experience on Business Growth, Sales generation, Leadership, Team Work, Motivation and Management. Dr. Amit Maheshwari has delivered more than 2500 speeches and seminars across the globe.
Dr. Amit Maheshwari can be seen or heard on national media (Aaj Tak, ABP News, News 24, Zee Business, NDTV Profit to name few), and national publications like Times of India, Hindustan Times, Navbharat Times, Amar Ujala and many others. He is a frequent guest writer in Gyan Publications and motivational poet who contributed his writings in Bollywood and National Media.
An in-demand speaker, Dr Amit’s practical experiences, proven research studies, creative use of latest technology and media, and his enthusiastic and passionate delivery, have proven to be a winning formula for millions of seminar attendees across the globe, including trips to Germany, France, Paris, Holland, Nepal, Dubai and many more.
 Dr. Amit Maheshwari also shares his knowledge through Video Blogging and Social Media. He is a famous Business Trainer and Motivational Blogger on YouTube and frequently post videos helping millions of Entrepreneurs, Industrialist, Manufacturers, Exporters, Brands Start-Ups and Youth to succeed and achieve their dreams. He is seen and followed by millions on Social Media.
Dr. Amit Maheshwari is a CEO- of Mettas Overseas Limited by the brand Name Mettas Lifestyle India’s Leading Manufacturer and Exporter of Stainless Steel Modular Kitchens, Wardrobes, Vanities Franchisee Showroom, Dealership Showroom and Associates network all over India and abroad.
